{"tid":2084431,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"七一如立國安法,最低風險遊行方式.","createTime":"2020-06-29T08:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T10:35:25.000Z","uid":259520,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"295b59120c0ed9b154c80dcfe78016f794942eb6","tid":2084431,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"七一如立國安法,最低風險遊行方式.<br />\n<br />\n如果堅持在香港遊行,咁以北角至中環碼頭之間,<br />\n來回遊行(守規則每路單一方向).<br />\n隨遊行者意願開始, 而目的地亦由遊行者自決.<br />\n但靜默遊行.<br />\n<br />\n咩野意思 =&gt; A君可由北角去銅鑼灣完結<br />\nB君可由銅鑼灣去金鐘完結<br />\nC君可由金鐘去銅鑼灣完結<br />\nD君可由銅鑼灣去北角完結<br />\n依照個人意願,可承風險!!<br />\n<br />\n令敵人兵力分散,多處要守, 變無處可守!!"},{"pid":"bfd8bbc623cec01c9068090eca50472fd3385cd5","tid":2084431,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"手足整咗過千個連豬襟章7.1派俾大家，大家唔係唔出呀嘛～<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2084344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2084344</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c4550e32e5207ee02b95206828723f9f341281b0","tid":2084431,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:41:53.000Z","msg":"一人一post推71<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Facebook Instagram airdrop都要post呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n可以一齊轉埋Icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSucHHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSucHHg.jpg&h=fe3ddeb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec63d71f36bc8ea5ca242712825ce97b4ddd2064","tid":2084431,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"唔好再諗咁多無謂嘢<br />\n喱d日子根本極少唔關事嘅人<br />\n狗見到你係港島遊行路線就拉得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n接受現實，唔會再有低風險遊行"},{"pid":"cc30aefc8cd292397035a9f9dc8e871f3657b7e8","tid":2084431,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:35:25.000Z","msg":"真係去既就要預左有機被拉.<br />\n因為呢幾次遊行都擺明九拉!!<br />\n呢個係事實.<br />\n<br />\n但咁樣都給拉,其實非法集結都好難落charge.<br />\n因為唔係同一方向,同一個點開始.<br />\n最大機會告你遊蕩罪!"}]}